org.sakaiproject.basiclti.util

Class SakaiBLTIUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.basiclti.util.SakaiBLTIUtil

  • public class SakaiBLTIUtil
extends Object
    Some Sakai Utility code for IMS Basic LTI This is mostly code to support the Sakai conventions for making and launching BLTI resources within Sakai.
